    <articleTitle>
      <Value><![CDATA[Gene Expression and Release of Growth Factors During Delayed Wound Healing: A Review of Studies in Diabetic Animals and Possible Combined Laser Phototherapy and Growth Factor Treatment to Enhance Healing]]></Value>
